text: Resurrection () is a 1960 Soviet drama movie directed by Mikhail Shveitser.Фестиваль «Литература и кино»: Догилева вывела дочь Екатерину в светВоскресение It stars Tamara Syomina, Yevgeny Matveyev, and Pavel Massalsky. ==Actors== *Tamara Syomina as Katyusha Maslova *Yevgeny Matveyev as Prince Nekhludov *Pavel Massalsky as Presiding Judge *Viktor Kulakov as Member of the Court *Vasili Bokarev as Member of the Court *Lev Zolotukhin as Prosecutor == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet movies Category:1960 movies Category:Soviet drama movies
